<a name="FUND:MCOAX"></a><a href="http://www.investools.com/cgi-bin/Library/t_page.pl/worth/MCOAX"><img src="/imgs/graph.gif" border=0><b>MainStay Convertible B </b></a>  15.4 5.0 240.4
Pacific Horizon Capital 14.0 4.5 196.3<p>NO-LOAD FUNDS
Fidelity Convertible Securities 11.9 0 953.1
SBSF Convertible Securities 9.8 0 59.5
Value Line Convertible 9.8 0 51.6<p>Source: Morningstar, Inc. All returns are annualized. Data as of 5/31/95. <p><p><p>
KEYWORDS: Bond Investing, Mutual Funds Investing

					</font>
